text: Kaltyayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kaltyayevsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 573 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 5 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Kaltyayevo
